                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Inspector of the Thames Police.</hi>) I heard a cry of "Police," and went on board the Limerick Lass, and took the prisoner—he</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184306120278"></xptr>
               <p>said he had brought two sailors, and one of them gave him 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. to put him on board a ship, and the other he supposed had gone adrift, or rowed away.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
